---
/**
 * Inline soft-ask strip. Lives at the bottom of long-read pages like
 * /research and /architecture. No "donate" language. Just attribution
 * and a low-pressure invite to chip in.
 */
---

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 mb-20">
  <div class="reveal glass rounded-xl px-6 py-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <span class="text-text-primary">This work is funded by people who think biology can beat backprop.</span>
        Compute, sensors, and runway, one supporter at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a
      href="/support"
      class="shrink-0 px-5 py-2 text-[12px] font-medium rounded-full border border-accent-amber/30 text-accent-amber hover:bg-accent-amber/10 hover:border-accent-amber/50 transition-all duration-300 font-mono tracking-wide text-center"
    >
      Support the build →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
